<br>
He frowned slightly and then moved to settle onto his throne.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/19/01 3:14:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enough</span><hr size=1> :<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> oesidon gets up and slowly walks away from the company with his head down in sorrow.::<br>
