<br>
Alecto went and sighed as she sat down in her throne of fire leaning her head in her hands.<br>
<br>
Megaera sat down n the middle of the floor.<br>
<br>
Tisiphone vanished in a whirl of black flames. Everyone knew where she was going. She was going to see the stone statues of her brothers and sisters. .. the Titans. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFF33>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23>The Olympian Gods</a> <font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href="http://www.amazonsunite.i-p.com">Home</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3 b4<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  